WEBVTT

00:00:01.193 --> 00:00:02.705
POLINA ZINGER

00:00:03.218 --> 00:00:05.186
EH KAUNAS LITVA

00:00:09.816 --> 00:00:13.337
in fir un fertsik, in toyznt nayn hundert fir un fertsikstn yor

00:00:13.613 --> 00:00:15.210
dem tsvelftn

00:00:15.283 --> 00:00:16.340
yuli

00:00:17.055 --> 00:00:19.563
hot men undz fun Shanzer lager

00:00:20.413 --> 00:00:22.110
aroysgefirt in Daytshland.

00:00:22.110 --> 00:00:25.160
UNK undz geheysn, oykhet UNK tsuzamen ⟨hot men⟩ in kolones

00:00:25.729 --> 00:00:28.372
un gefirt durkh Ponemuner brik.

00:00:28.446 --> 00:00:30.785
beshas m'hot undz gefirt durkh Ponemuner brik

00:00:31.180 --> 00:00:33.891
hobn mir geklert "oyber m'vet undz firn"

00:00:34.082 --> 00:00:39.071
azoy hobn mir gemeynt "⟨oyber m'vet undz⟩ firn oyf links, oyfn Ponemun dortn in di velder, vet men undz shisn.

00:00:39.229 --> 00:00:44.572
oyber oyf rekhts, ken zayn m'vet men undz in di vagones firn, un avekfirn in Daytshland, in di lagern.

00:00:45.169 --> 00:00:46.921
endikt ⟨oyf⟩, durkhn brik

00:00:46.921 --> 00:00:49.230
eyner a yunger yingl

00:00:49.573 --> 00:00:53.029
vayzt oys az er hot zikh dershrokn, zikh gemeynt az me firt undz tsum s- shisn

00:00:53.029 --> 00:00:54.565
hot er getantst fun brik

00:00:54.565 --> 00:00:55.642
in Nyeman.

00:00:55.817 --> 00:00:57.071
er hot gants

00:00:57.071 --> 00:01:00.952
oyf, oyf, vey- nit, nit veynik hot er geshvumen. mir hobn aleyn gezen.

00:01:00.952 --> 00:01:02.679
un oyfn tsveyte zayt breg

00:01:03.259 --> 00:01:05.213
hot men genumen oyf im shisn

00:01:05.213 --> 00:01:08.332
ver hot im geshosn, ⟨mir hobn⟩ nit gezen, vayle s'iz geven vayt

00:01:08.743 --> 00:01:12.210
un m'hot im getrofn, hobn mir aleyn gezen, un er iz arunter tsum

00:01:12.210 --> 00:01:14.200
tsum, me

00:01:14.262 --> 00:01:16.393
tsum m- UNK

00:01:15.898 --> 00:01:16.803
grunt.

00:01:16.393 --> 00:01:17.849
tsum grunt iz er arunter.

00:01:18.379 --> 00:01:19.987
un mir zaynen vayter gegangen.

00:01:19.987 --> 00:01:22.507
gegangen zaynen mir. ⟨m'hot men⟩ gefirt

00:01:23.138 --> 00:01:28.593
mir hobn, oyf, oyf a barg zaynen mir aroyfgegangen dortn, vayzt oys tsu, tsu di vagones. s'iz geshtanen

00:01:28.593 --> 00:01:31.501
vagones vu me firt beheymes

00:01:32.368 --> 00:01:35.281
un m'hot undz alemen geheysn araynen in di vagones.

00:01:36.402 --> 00:01:41.032
geyendik shoyn, vos mir hobn nokh gehat geblibn fun di lagern, etlekhe zakhn vos UNK

00:01:41.032 --> 00:01:45.112
hobn mir alts gevorfn, vayl s'iz geven zeyer heys un zeyer shver, mir zaynen shoyn geven opgeshvakht tsu geyn.

00:01:45.835 --> 00:01:49.020
arayngefirt ⟨hot tsu⟩ undz in di vagones, hot men undz arayngepakt

00:01:49.020 --> 00:01:51.630
UNK mir gevezn in di vagones vi hering in a fas.

00:01:51.797 --> 00:01:54.041
eyner lebn di andere gezesn.

00:01:54.041 --> 00:01:56.324
di vagones, di vagones hot men farklapt.

00:01:56.652 --> 00:02:01.222
keyn luft iz nit gevezn mit vos tsum atemen. a gantse nakht zaynen mir geforn

00:02:01.222 --> 00:02:02.327
gezesn

00:02:02.327 --> 00:02:05.133
on trinken un on vaser, on keyn zakh.

00:02:05.511 --> 00:02:08.829
m'iz geven tsum khaleshn, un etlekhe hobn gekhalesht in di vagones.

00:02:09.509 --> 00:02:13.537
di f- di, di, di f- di, di tirn flegt men nit efenen

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:17.958
UNK di kleyne fensterlekh oybn iz gevezn. mir hobn afile gezen vu me firt undz un vos me firt undz.

00:02:18.943 --> 00:02:22.180
az di daytshn hobn gezogt az ir darf a- avekgeyn fun dem

00:02:22.180 --> 00:02:26.058
Shanser lager, hobn zey gezogt az zey firn aykh epes vu avek?

00:02:25.069 --> 00:02:27.358
m'hot undz, zey hobn gezogt az me firt undz oyf arbet.

00:02:27.567 --> 00:02:29.096
avu hot men nisht gezogt?

00:02:28.562 --> 00:02:30.884
neyn, nit gezogt. me firt undz oyf arbet.

00:02:32.393 --> 00:02:35.796
mit eyn vort, m'hot undz gefirt durkh, vayzt oys durkh nakht

00:02:36.426 --> 00:02:37.770
un oyf morgn

00:02:38.417 --> 00:02:42.380
hot men undz, mir zaynen geforn z- gantse, mayn- undzer gantse mishpokhe

00:02:42.380 --> 00:02:44.580
vayle got hot undz di gantse tsayt geholfn, un

00:02:44.580 --> 00:02:46.950
⟨dem⟩ gantse geto, nokh ale aktsyes

00:02:46.950 --> 00:02:50.430
hot men undz nit tsesheydt. mir ale geblibn, der foter mit di muter

00:02:50.430 --> 00:02:51.790
un der bruder un ikh.

00:02:51.968 --> 00:02:53.767
vayzt oys iz gevezn aza min goyrl.

00:02:54.533 --> 00:02:57.373
az mir zaynen ⟨nit⟩ gekumen in

00:02:57.373 --> 00:02:59.302
vu mir zaynen gekumen hobn mir nit gevust.

00:03:00.523 --> 00:03:04.702
⟨nare⟩ m'hot undz gefirt, UNK aroysgef- aroysgetribn ale fun di vagones

00:03:04.810 --> 00:03:07.436
un mir hobn gezen a groysn, groysn

00:03:07.881 --> 00:03:08.769
toyer

00:03:09.872 --> 00:03:11.334
vos iz geven oyfgeshribn

00:03:12.825 --> 00:03:16.987
ARBEIT MACHT UNS FREI UNK iz dortn geven oyfgeshribn. umgefer azoy.

00:03:17.837 --> 00:03:19.299
men hot tseteylt

00:03:19.305 --> 00:03:20.407
di mener

00:03:20.407 --> 00:03:21.510
mit di froyen.

00:03:22.191 --> 00:03:24.240
zaynen geven dortn kinder oykhet. ya.

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:26.830
di kinder velkhe zey zaynen durkhgegangen

00:03:26.830 --> 00:03:32.732
durkh di kinder aktsye, velkhe ⟨di⟩ eltern hobn oysbahaltn di kinder, velkhe m'hot zey tsugenumen ⟨durkh⟩ di kinder aktsye

00:03:32.856 --> 00:03:36.114
iz di eltern zaynen ge- in di vagones geven mit zeyere kinder.

00:03:36.114 --> 00:03:40.394
tsum bayshpil, mayn tante, di tante LYUBA Vald

00:03:40.488 --> 00:03:42.251
un der onkl Abe Vald

00:03:42.251 --> 00:03:43.910
hobn gehat tsvey kinder.

00:03:43.910 --> 00:03:46.010
zey, beshas s'iz geven di kinder aktsye

00:03:46.010 --> 00:03:48.120
hobn zey di kinder zeyere oysbahaltn

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:55.862
vu z- eyner baym moy- dakht zikh mir az zey hobn eynem a- di meydele hobn zey far⟨UNK⟩ in a zekele oyfgehangen oyfn vant. vi dem yingele gedenk ikh ⟨nit vu⟩ m'hot im bahaltn.

00:03:55.862 --> 00:03:57.971
ober zey hobn zeyere kinder oysbahaltn.

00:03:57.971 --> 00:04:00.694
un zey mit di kinder zaynen gekumen tsuzamen in

00:04:00.767 --> 00:04:01.734
Daytshland.

00:04:01.734 --> 00:04:03.275
dos iz in Poyln vayzt oys gevezn.

00:04:03.248 --> 00:04:07.410
dertseylt a bisele, vi UNK vi hot dos oysgezen di kinder aktsye?

00:04:07.298 --> 00:04:11.781
beshas s'iz geven di kinder aktsye hob ikh nit gezen, vayl mir ale zaynen geven oyf der arbet.

00:04:11.888 --> 00:04:14.767
di kinder aktsye iz forgekumen beshas mir zaynen gevezn

00:04:14.807 --> 00:04:15.948
oyf der arbet

00:04:15.954 --> 00:04:19.588
un beshas in, in, in Sha- beshas ikh bin geven dan in Shanser lager.

00:04:19.588 --> 00:04:21.466
in Shanser lager iz oykh geven a kinder aktsye.

00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:26.192
un beshas mir zaynen geven oyf, oyf der arbet iz in lager geblibn nokh eltere mentshn

00:04:26.586 --> 00:04:28.284
un di kinder.

00:04:28.712 --> 00:04:30.343
az mir zaynen gekumen

00:04:30.383 --> 00:04:31.860
hobn mir shoyn di kinder nit gefunen.

00:04:31.860 --> 00:04:34.706
beshas di eltern zaynen gekumen un nit gefunen di kinder

00:04:34.706 --> 00:04:38.446
hot zikh ongehoybn a shreklekhe geveyneray, a shreklekhe shrayeray.

00:04:38.446 --> 00:04:40.716
eyne gedenk ikh lebn undzer nare iz gezesn

00:04:40.716 --> 00:04:43.090
⟨tsi Kaplan⟩ UNK geven ⟨tsi vi ikh⟩ gedenk nit

00:04:43.090 --> 00:04:45.000
hot er genumen zikh klapn di kop on vant.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:46.900
er hot gehat zeyer a sheynem yingele

00:04:46.900 --> 00:04:48.510
un er iz gekumen, hot nit gefunen dem kind.

00:04:49.975 --> 00:04:54.381
azoy arum az ver es hot oysbahaltn di kinder in Shans, in, in lager

00:04:54.381 --> 00:04:56.631
un in Shanser lager, un in geto

00:04:56.631 --> 00:04:59.481
iz men gekumen mit zey in STUTTHOF.

00:04:59.239 --> 00:05:01.781
ven iz forgekumen di kinder aktsye in ge-

00:05:00.943 --> 00:05:04.973
⟨ven⟩ forgekumen? in

00:05:03.627 --> 00:05:04.768
umgefer.

00:05:04.973 --> 00:05:08.333
in dray un fertsikstn yor, neyn? tsi fir un fertsikstn?

00:05:08.368 --> 00:05:10.032
un vi ir gedenkt nit genoy?

00:05:09.634 --> 00:05:11.383
genoy gedenk ikh nit.

00:05:11.457 --> 00:05:13.661
ober ir zayt shoyn dan geven in Shanser lager.

00:05:13.279 --> 00:05:15.216
mir zaynen dan geven in Shanser lager, ya.

00:05:15.216 --> 00:05:16.917
in Shanser lager zaynen mir dan gevezn.

00:05:17.211 --> 00:05:19.351
iz gevezn dos.

00:05:19.351 --> 00:05:22.161
dan hot men undz aroysgefirt in, in

00:05:22.161 --> 00:05:23.691
in ST- in STUTTHOF.

00:05:23.691 --> 00:05:26.491
in STUTTHOF az mir zaynen gekumen in STUTTHOF, hot men glaykh tseteylt

00:05:26.491 --> 00:05:28.331
di mener mit di froyen.

00:05:28.331 --> 00:05:29.822
di mener in eyn ort

00:05:29.822 --> 00:05:33.388
un undz hot men arayngefirt in STUTTHOF, un zey hot men arayngefirt in DACHAU.

00:05:34.153 --> 00:05:37.066
ir hot dos gevust az zey firt men avek in an ander ort?

00:05:37.107 --> 00:05:39.643
mir hobn gevust az me firt zey avek in an ander lager.

00:05:39.643 --> 00:05:41.622
ober in velkhn lager hobn mir nit gevust.

00:05:41.899 --> 00:05:47.110
nor beshas me hot undz tseteylt dem foter mit di muter, der foter m- undz, di mener mit di froyen

00:05:47.110 --> 00:05:51.430
hobn mir gezogt UNK, der foter hot gezogt "oyber mir veln bl- ver es vet fun undz blaybn lebn

00:05:51.430 --> 00:05:53.720
iz undzer tref ort in Kovne."

00:05:55.568 --> 00:05:57.705
un azoy zaynen mir arayn in

00:05:57.711 --> 00:05:58.565
STUTTHOF.

00:05:59.196 --> 00:06:01.724
vi dem ershtn ⟨may in⟩

00:06:01.724 --> 00:06:06.682
UNK iz gevezn az mir hot men arayngefirt in STUTTHOF hob ikh gezen a groysn barg mit shikh.

00:06:06.756 --> 00:06:09.399
geven zeyer in ordenung tsuzamengeshtaplt

00:06:09.473 --> 00:06:10.716
punkt vi

00:06:10.907 --> 00:06:11.913
holts

00:06:11.920 --> 00:06:14.749
zeyer a groyser shtapl iz geven fun shikh.

00:06:14.822 --> 00:06:16.692
shpeter geven fun kleyder

00:06:16.692 --> 00:06:19.662
hobn mir glaykh farshtanen azoy mir shoyn gehat gevust

00:06:19.662 --> 00:06:22.282
un, un dort geven a krematorium gezogt UNK STUTTHOF

00:06:22.282 --> 00:06:24.872
az dortn iz UNK farbrent gevorn di ale mentshn

00:06:24.872 --> 00:06:27.652
vos di shikh ⟨un⟩ dos lign zi shoyn vayzt oys di mentshn nito.

00:06:28.980 --> 00:06:31.912
undz gebrakht in STUTTHOF, hot men undz glaykh

00:06:31.912 --> 00:06:33.852
genumen traybn.

00:06:33.852 --> 00:06:35.454
"SCHNELL, SCHNELL. BEWEGT EUCH."

00:06:36.591 --> 00:06:38.930
genumen alemen farshraybn.

00:06:39.038 --> 00:06:40.348
m'hot undz farshribn.

00:06:41.350 --> 00:06:44.888
genumen, oysgeton ale zakhn.

00:06:46.682 --> 00:06:48.431
gegebn hefling zakhn

00:06:51.525 --> 00:06:54.455
un avekgefirt in di barakes.

00:06:56.098 --> 00:07:01.391
antshuldikt, ab- ah, ir hot UNK arumgevashn dortn, tsi me hot dos nisht gegebn?

00:07:01.093 --> 00:07:02.184
m'hot gegebn.

00:07:02.275 --> 00:07:06.684
m'hot gegebn tsum vashn zikh, arumvash- mir hobn gemeynt az me firt undz shoyn gor in krematorium

00:07:06.684 --> 00:07:10.000
mir hobn gemeynt az s'iz gaz kameres, vayl mir hobn shoyn alts gevust, m'hot alts ⟨getseylt⟩

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:11.181
ya, rikhtik nokh

00:07:11.181 --> 00:07:13.029
un beshas mir hobn UNK gefirt

00:07:13.029 --> 00:07:14.233
hobn mir gezen

00:07:14.273 --> 00:07:15.763
a sakh froyen

00:07:15.763 --> 00:07:19.259
farbay, a g- groyse kolone froyen, farbay lebn UNK farbay undz

00:07:19.259 --> 00:07:21.559
in gantsn, mir zaynen geven nokh mit hor in geto

00:07:21.576 --> 00:07:22.709
on hor

00:07:22.709 --> 00:07:25.409
zeyer vilde blikn azelkhene

00:07:25.528 --> 00:07:27.708
oysgemagerte zeyer di froyen

00:07:27.708 --> 00:07:30.148
un zey hobn alts gezogt "ungar, ungar."

00:07:30.148 --> 00:07:33.068
mir hobn gemeynt az zey zogn "hunger, hunger," az zey zaynen azoy

00:07:33.068 --> 00:07:35.038
fun hunger UNK

00:07:35.038 --> 00:07:36.988
nokh dem farshtanen az zey fun Ungarn.

00:07:36.988 --> 00:07:39.118
zey hot men gebrakht fun OSWIECIM.

00:07:39.118 --> 00:07:41.939
iz zeyer a shreklekher lager, zaynen geven zeyer tseshrokene

00:07:41.939 --> 00:07:43.939
hot men zey gebrakht do in STUTTHOF.

00:07:46.082 --> 00:07:49.791
az undz ⟨hot men⟩ gebrakht in STUTTHOF, hobn mir gevust az do iz shoyn keyn

00:07:49.791 --> 00:07:53.366
ya, m'hot glaykh opgeteylt. dos iz geven a shreklekher

00:07:53.912 --> 00:07:55.391
harts raysnde

00:07:55.583 --> 00:07:57.180
stsene iz gevezn

00:07:57.186 --> 00:08:00.656
beshas men hot genumen di froyen mit di kinder opteyln

00:08:00.713 --> 00:08:02.749
di froyen mit kinder in eyn ort

00:08:02.856 --> 00:08:04.742
un undz froyen on

00:08:04.742 --> 00:08:05.966
yunge froyen

00:08:05.966 --> 00:08:09.178
meydlekh in a tsveyte ort. un mayn tante, LYUBA Vald

00:08:09.252 --> 00:08:10.697
mit di meydele

00:08:11.057 --> 00:08:13.981
mit ir kind. gevezn vayzt oys oyfn hant. ikh veys nit, hot zi

00:08:13.981 --> 00:08:15.531
tsvey yor, tsi gevezn dray ts-

00:08:15.531 --> 00:08:17.001
tsvey yor vayzt oys iz zi gevezn

00:08:17.001 --> 00:08:19.601
tsi onderhalbn yor. kh'ken nit zogn geshtimt

00:08:20.659 --> 00:08:24.560
zi iz, mit ir oyfn hant, hot zi mir gezogt "POLA

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:26.550
tsulib mayn kind gey ikh

00:08:26.550 --> 00:08:29.280
in GAZOVYY kamer.

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:32.370
ikh ze shoyn vos do tut zikh. ikh veys shoyn vos do vet zayn."

00:08:33.568 --> 00:08:41.797
UNK hot men opgeteylt, glaykh UNK sh- ⟨shtekhldrot⟩ UNK in eyn tsayt un undz in a tsveyte zayt, un mer hob ikh ir shoyn nokh nit gezen, un nokh di milkhome iz UNK nit gekumen.

00:08:42.275 --> 00:08:47.062
der onkl mayner vos er iz geven in DACHAU iz oykh avekgeforn mitn yingele, mit UZIEL hot er geheysn.

00:08:48.553 --> 00:08:51.977
un dortn beshas ⟨efsher⟩ nokh di milkhome hob ikh im dem onkl getrofn

00:08:51.977 --> 00:08:55.887
hot er gezogt az dem yingele hot men fun im oykh tsugenumen, avekgefirt in gaz kamer.

00:08:56.130 --> 00:09:00.123
azoy arum az beyde kinder hobn zey nit gekent oysbahaltn.

00:09:00.717 --> 00:09:03.228
nit gut UNK ⟨oyf⟩ dem vos zey hobn in geton zikh oysbahaltn.

00:09:06.070 --> 00:09:08.409
nu, undz ⟨hot men⟩ gebrakht in STUTTHOF

00:09:08.922 --> 00:09:09.889
geven dortn

00:09:09.889 --> 00:09:12.392
ge- keyn, m'iz shoyn keyn, dortn keyn mentsh nit gevezn.

00:09:12.803 --> 00:09:15.902
zikh geshpirt far, far nit keyn mentsh. far gornisht.

00:09:16.498 --> 00:09:18.179
"gey do, shtey do"

00:09:18.220 --> 00:09:21.217
far, far di klenste zakh, "shteyst nit azoy," a klap.

00:09:21.257 --> 00:09:23.951
"nemst nit azoy di shisele tsum esn," vider a klap.

00:09:25.037 --> 00:09:28.743
"loyfst nit azoy gikh tsu tsu, tsu dem vash roym," vider a klap.

00:09:29.104 --> 00:09:32.338
di kapos di froyen zaynen dokh geven nokh ergere vi di mener.

00:09:33.812 --> 00:09:36.202
ni- far yeder zakh flegstu krign klep.

00:09:38.352 --> 00:09:39.570
eyn mol

00:09:39.570 --> 00:09:43.907
bay nakht UNK gevezn UNK, flegn UNK avekgeleygt oyf di nare shlofn

00:09:43.937 --> 00:09:46.259
vos heyst shoyn shlofn, lign.

00:09:47.059 --> 00:09:50.124
di kapo iz gekumen. vayzt oys iz geven a polyatshke.

00:09:51.582 --> 00:09:55.155
hot oysgegosn di vaser, a emer tsi mit a SCHLAUCH vaser UNK

00:09:55.155 --> 00:09:56.855
mir dakht zikh az a emer vaser

00:09:56.855 --> 00:09:58.385
hot zi oysgegosn oyfn dil

00:09:58.838 --> 00:10:03.641
undz alemen geheysn oyfshteyn. "ver hot do di vaser oysgegosn? gikh leyg zikh aleyn in di vaser."

00:10:05.436 --> 00:10:07.134
m'hot geleygt in di vaser

00:10:07.495 --> 00:10:10.391
oyfgeshtanen. "itster makht reyn un geyt ts- leygt zikh vider avek."

00:10:10.802 --> 00:10:14.036
azoy arum az m'iz shoyn, m'iz shoyn gevezn nit keyn mentshn.

00:10:16.185 --> 00:10:17.816
azoy hobn mir gelitn

00:10:18.717 --> 00:10:19.808
in STUTTHOF

00:10:20.573 --> 00:10:23.725
nit keyn sakh. di shtarkere, di yingere

00:10:23.725 --> 00:10:28.110
hot men vi bay, opgeteylt undz. di mame hot men gelozn in STUTTHOF

00:10:28.977 --> 00:10:31.848
di eltere hot men gelozn in STUTTHOF, un undz di yingere

00:10:31.848 --> 00:10:34.928
hot men avekgefirt oyf arbet, ⟨fun⟩ STUTTHOF oyf arbet.

