fun, fun rey un zaynen geblibn in STETTIN.

00:20:13.865 --> 00:20:18.490
shpeter nokh di milkhome UNK zeyer gezukht durkhn roytn kreyts, ⟨gezukht⟩ umetum, in ergets ⟨zey⟩ nit gefunen.

