un azoy flegn mir shlofn vu s'iz geven kalt, shreklekh

00:20:39.789 --> 00:20:42.903
UNK zaynen mir geven farlayzikt, farshmutst

00:20:42.903 --> 00:20:43.879
hungerik

00:20:44.982 --> 00:20:49.279
un dos letste iz gevezn dos ergste, beshas me hot undz arayngefirt

00:20:49.504 --> 00:20:51.219
in a groysn shtal.

