vayl keyn vaser iz shoyn nit gevezn

00:22:37.598 --> 00:22:40.388
un di shney iz geven zeyer shmutsik, vayle s'iz nit gevezn keyn tualetn arum

00:22:40.388 --> 00:22:41.958
flegt men geyn arum shtal

00:22:42.010 --> 00:22:44.690
un di shney iz geven sh- alts eyns flegt men esn. geven disenterye

00:22:44.690 --> 00:22:48.315
dortn glaykh beshas di, m'hot undz bafrayt, hot men glaykh gemakht a karantin

00:22:48.315 --> 00:22:51.715
un keynem hot men UNK nit aroysgelozn un keynem hot men nit arayngelozn

00:22:51.831 --> 00:22:53.529
vayl s'iz geven nokh epidemye.

00:22:54.565 --> 00:22:56.280
beshas men hot geendikt

00:22:57.045 --> 00:22:59.283
beshas s'iz shoyn gevezn tsum ende

00:23:00.133 --> 00:23:04.366
un eyne, un di Taybele hot tsu mir tsugevorfn un gezogt "POLA

00:23:04.366 --> 00:23:06.926
heyb zikh oyf, ⟨vet men⟩ kumen loyfn. me zogt az mit dem sh-

00:23:06.926 --> 00:23:09.336
-tal veln, me vil untertsindn dem shtal.

00:23:09.336 --> 00:23:10.636
kum rateven zikh."

