s'loyft, es efnt zikh di tir. geyt araynen a froy mit zeyer a vilde shtime

00:23:29.796 --> 00:23:31.262
nit keyn geherike

00:23:31.757 --> 00:23:34.012
"vayber, froyen

00:23:34.204 --> 00:23:36.408
kh'hob aleyn gezen arum shoyn tank."

00:23:37.680 --> 00:23:41.530
zog ikh nor tsu LENA, zog ikh "LENA" zog ikh, "kh'ze zi iz arunter fun zinen.

