"babinke" zogt er

00:24:17.978 --> 00:24:19.037
"halt zikh.

00:24:19.037 --> 00:24:23.844
bald vet kumen SANITARNAYA CHAST', un m'vet aykh bald tsuzamennemen alemen.

00:24:24.272 --> 00:24:25.666
ligt, halt zikh."

00:24:27.023 --> 00:24:31.742
mit eyn vort LENA mayn kuz- mayn shvegerin hot gezogt "POLA" zogt zi

00:24:32.507 --> 00:24:34.200
"⟨ir vel ikh⟩ efsher nokh tsugeyn

00:24:34.200 --> 00:24:36.011
tsum, in shtetl" zogt zi.

00:24:36.152 --> 00:24:39.979
"un ikh vel dir brengen a por shlyures oder sh- kaloshn

00:24:39.979 --> 00:24:43.216
un ikh vel dir nemen, un ikh vel dir avekfirn in shtetl" zogt zi.

00:24:43.273 --> 00:24:46.220
"vos vestu do lign durkh nakht?" zogt zi. "du vest avekshtarbn."

00:24:46.750 --> 00:24:49.292
zog ikh LENA zog ikh, "oyber du kenst" zog ikh "gey.

00:24:49.332 --> 00:24:50.878
ikh vel dir vartn oyf dir."

00:24:51.677 --> 00:24:52.970
iz zi avek in der fri

00:24:54.343 --> 00:24:55.332
bay tog

00:24:55.828 --> 00:25:00.310
eyne iz geshtorbn, a tsveyte, fun ir a ku- ir LENA's a kuzine, a meydl mit, mit

00:25:00.310 --> 00:25:03.480
mit groyse tsep hot zi gehat lange. fun a shtetl iz zi gevezn

00:25:03.507 --> 00:25:05.798
ikh ze zi iz dortn UNK "ikh vel a kuk gebn oyf ir" zog ikh

00:25:05.798 --> 00:25:09.108
vi hot zi geheysn, Rivele, ⟨tsu ir⟩ gezogt "Rivele, du lebst?" zi hot shoyn nit geentfert.

00:25:09.108 --> 00:25:11.318
"vel ikh vartn UNK. oyb UNK durkhlebn

00:25:11.318 --> 00:25:13.948
di nakht, vel ikh shoyn oykh nit oys." UNK zi vet nit kumen.

00:25:13.948 --> 00:25:15.678
s'iz geven a UNK nakht

00:25:15.859 --> 00:25:16.927
ikh her me zogt

00:25:16.927 --> 00:25:18.418
"POLA, du lebst?"

