zog ikh "LENA, ikh bin do. ikh bin, ikh lig nokh do."

00:25:22.407 --> 00:25:23.683
hot zi mir gebrakht

00:25:24.229 --> 00:25:25.027
aza min

00:25:25.027 --> 00:25:27.210
banke mit konservirte hun.

00:25:28.178 --> 00:25:29.809
zi hot dortn gefunen in shtub

00:25:30.405 --> 00:25:31.951
un der por kaloshn

00:25:33.645 --> 00:25:35.465
zogt zi "kum, n- es di hun."

00:25:35.465 --> 00:25:40.235
zog ikh "neyn." zog ikh "LENA, ikh vil nit esn. UNK shney, breng mir shney. khotsh a hoyfn shney breng mir."

00:25:40.952 --> 00:25:42.780
UNK hot mir gegebn shney

00:25:42.780 --> 00:25:46.065
un gezogt "est a shtikele hun." zog ikh "neyn, ikh ken nit esn." UNK

00:25:46.065 --> 00:25:49.375
un ikh UNK arayn shoyn UNK kaloshn, un mir zaynen gegangen tsu ⟨CHINOW⟩.

00:25:50.048 --> 00:25:56.203
geyendik, mistame geven a kilometer tsu geyn, un efsher veyniker, UNK ⟨oystsukumen aza⟩ kilometer tsu geyn tsu, in shtetl.

00:25:56.203 --> 00:25:58.193
geyendik tsu di shtetl

00:25:58.654 --> 00:26:00.279
zeen mir, eyn froy ligt

00:26:00.279 --> 00:26:01.056
oyf UNK

00:26:01.056 --> 00:26:03.283
shoyn in di shney, a geshtorbene

00:26:03.283 --> 00:26:06.225
a tsveyte ligt in, in tsayt fun bafrayen

00:26:06.349 --> 00:26:10.646
geshtorbn. nit der- nit derlebt, nit dervart.

00:26:11.344 --> 00:26:13.582
arayngegangen zaynen mir in shtetl

00:26:14.331 --> 00:26:15.787
in ershte shtub.

00:26:15.787 --> 00:26:17.171
di shtub iz geven a puste.

00:26:17.171 --> 00:26:19.219
vayzt oys ale zaynen UNK antlofn.

00:26:19.326 --> 00:26:20.434
gehat moyre

00:26:20.473 --> 00:26:21.445
far der armey.

00:26:22.684 --> 00:26:26.292
in a shtu- in, in ershtn tsimer zaynen mir arayngegangen in, in tsimer

00:26:26.292 --> 00:26:28.955
oyfn, oyfn tir zaynen shoyn gelegn tsvey froyen

00:26:29.923 --> 00:26:33.275
oyfn, oyfn bet do, in der zayt iz gelegn vider tsvey froyen

00:26:33.484 --> 00:26:35.807
do oyfn SOFA iz gelegn vider tsvey froyen

