s'iz nit geven zikh avu nit oyf, avu avektsuzetsn. s'iz geven, in der zayt iz geshtanen a shafe.

00:26:41.179 --> 00:26:43.468
kh'hob geefnt di tir un zikh avekgezetst in shafe.

00:26:43.558 --> 00:26:46.066
un ikh bin geze- gezesn durkh nakht in shafe.

00:26:48.283 --> 00:26:51.962
s'iz arayngeg- alts flegn farbaygeyn di soldatn. di armey flegt farbaygeyn.

00:26:51.962 --> 00:26:53.572
di ershte, di tankistn.

