00:26:56.082 --> 00:26:56.952
"halt zikh

00:26:56.952 --> 00:26:58.992
es vet kumen SANATARNAYA CHAST', m'vet aykh gebn."

00:26:58.992 --> 00:26:59.962
eyner hot gebrakht

00:27:00.366 --> 00:27:05.527
geg- UNK tsu mir get- gegebn vos tsu trinken, UNK shnaps, tsi tsi tsi tsi tsi, tsi spirt tsi vos

00:27:05.527 --> 00:27:08.567
"nem a g- nem a g- nem a" zogt er "a top, es vet vern dir beser."

00:27:08.297 --> 00:27:09.168
shlung

00:27:08.567 --> 00:27:10.586
a sh- a shlung ⟨vet dir⟩ vern beser.

