efsher hob ikh ⟨im⟩ getrunken. ikh veys nit.

00:27:14.592 --> 00:27:19.361
un az ikh bin UNK s'iz dort gezesn, di vos zaynen geven shtarker zaynen arunter, fun tish zaynen arunter

00:27:19.958 --> 00:27:22.351
un mir hobn zikh shoyn avekgeleygt oyfn tish.

00:27:22.351 --> 00:27:25.381
di s- di fus hot mi- di fus hot mir zeyer vey geton

00:27:25.381 --> 00:27:27.208
vayl mir iz geven opgefrorn di fis.

00:27:28.277 --> 00:27:32.032
mir hobn genumen klern vi mir shoyn UNK oyfn tish darf men shoyn lign

