mir hobn genumen glaykh dem laylekh ⟨oykhet⟩.

00:27:43.980 --> 00:27:44.859
UNK

00:27:44.899 --> 00:27:46.952
un ⟨farviklt un⟩ aroysgevorfn durkhn fentster.

