genumen a tsveytn laylekh. vider avekgeleygt. vider hobn mir aroysgevorfn.

00:27:50.552 --> 00:27:54.089
vayl s'iz geven ful, s'flegt fun undz krikhn ful layz.

00:27:56.172 --> 00:28:01.060
nokh dem fun, fun, fun, fun be- fun bet eyne iz shoyn aroysgegangen, hob ikh shoyn avekgeleygt in, in bet.

