farvundet

00:28:41.776 --> 00:28:43.856
un zey makhn di ale, zey makhn a shpitol

00:28:43.856 --> 00:28:46.076
un zey brengen zey in shpitol.

00:28:46.076 --> 00:28:48.832
un zey m- zey makhn vayzt oys tsu reyn vos iz nit reyn.

00:28:49.918 --> 00:28:53.425
dos iz a militerishe m- t- SANITARNAYA CHAST' zaynen militerishe mentshn.

